projects.name: NGO APP
projects.description: Developed a mobile application called NGO APP designed to combat food waste and provide assistance to those in need. The app uses innovative algorithms to connect surplus food from various sources with individuals facing hunger, effectively reducing food waste while addressing a critical societal issue.

projects.name: Hostel Ease
projects.description: Developed the HostelEase mobile application, a comprehensive solution for efficient hostel management. HostelEase streamlines key hostel operations, offering features such as student attendance tracking, a student assistance portal, and real-time access to mess menus and hostel facilities. This app simplifies hostel management tasks and enhances the overall student living experience.
